       7.1  LLLLiiiisssstttt WWWWiiiiddddggggeeeetttt

       The List widget allows you to make a selection from a list
       of items.  The application defines an array of compound
       strings, each of which becomes an item in the list.  You can
       set the number of items in the list that are to be visible.
       You can also choose to have the List appear with a ScrollBar
       so that you can scroll through the list of items.  Items are
       selected by moving the pointer to the desired item and
       pressing the mouse button or key defined as select.  The      |
       selected item is displayed in inverse color.

